data.description:
Step into this stunning 4-bedroom, 2-bath sanctuary, spread across two expansive stories. Every element in this BIC-crafted home has been thoughtfully designed for modern living. Graceful window shutters enhance the beauty while the refrigerated AC ensures a comfortable haven, year-round.

Discover convenience with a primary bedroom tucked away on the ground floor, offering both privacy and ease of access. The upper level reveals a versatile loft space—perfect for an office, playroom, or cozy reading nook.

Outdoors, a generously-sized backyard beckons, offering ample space for family gatherings, gardening, or weekend relaxation. The double garage provides ample storage, while RV owners will appreciate dedicated parking complete with essential hook-ups.
Location, and a layout that truly understands the homeowner's needs—this is not just a home, it's a lifestyle. Experience the best of contemporary living & schedule your showing to view it today.
